text: End of season is defined as the last day in the season (1st October - 30th April) with more than 10mm of rainfall.

zm_ny: Kutha kwa nyengo akutanthauza tsiku lomaliza mu nyengo (1 okotobala mpaka 30 epulo) lomwe kwagwa mvula yoposa 10mm

text: Length of season is defined as the total days from the start of the season until the end of the season as defined

text: Seasonal rainfall is defined as the total rain recorded from the start of the season until the end of the season

text: Start of season is defined as the first occasion (from 1st October) with more than 25mm in a 3 day period and no dry spell of 10 days or more within the following 30 days
